"lazy" class="VrWOfVJtTjn2FNJx0TFc" /><span class="QGnVckPD11ZTkQr8o8ci">西瓜游戏</span></a><a href="/zh/恐龙" class="DIxbY_Wd8M99mMzbD9Jz Ll7V72dm63WTr1buD4lg"><img src="https://img.poki-cdn.com/cdn-cgi/image/q=78,scq=50,width=94,height=94,fit=cover,f=auto/caf90442dc36b16784f9bfe7a913370f/恐龙-logo.png" srcSet="https://img.poki-cdn.com/cdn-cgi/image/q=78,scq=50,width=94,height=94,fit=cover,f=auto/caf90442dc36b16784f9bfe7a913370f/恐龙-logo.png 1x, https://img.poki-cdn.com/cdn-cgi/image/q=78,scq=50,width=188,height=188,fit=cover,f=auto/caf90442dc36b16784f9bfe7a913370f/恐龙-logo.png 2x" width="94" height="94" alt="恐龙游戏" loading="lazy" class="VrWOfVJtTjn2FNJx0TFc" /><span class="QGnVckPD11ZTkQr8o8ci">恐龙游戏</span></a><a href="/zh/养鱼" class="DIxbY_Wd8M99mMzbD9Jz Ll7V72dm63WTr1buD4lg"><img src="https://img.poki-cdn.com/cdn-cgi/image/q=78,scq=50,width=94,height=94,fit=cover,f=auto/117509765d91fa66d75858808c063b96/养鱼-logo.png" srcSet="https://img.poki-cdn.com/cdn-cgi/image/q=78,scq=50,width=94,height=94,fit=cover,f=auto/117509765d91fa66d75858808c063b96/养鱼-logo.png 1x, https://img.poki-cdn.com/cdn-cgi/image/q=78,scq=50,width=188,height=188,fit=cover,f=auto/117509765d91fa66d75858808c063b96/养鱼-logo.png 2x" width="94" height="94" alt="养鱼游戏" loading="lazy" class="VrWOfVJtTjn2FNJx0TFc" /><span class="QGnVckPD11ZTkQr8o8ci">养鱼游戏</span></a><a href="/zh/打字" class="DIxbY_Wd8M99mMzbD9Jz Ll7V72dm63WTr1buD4lg"><img src="https://img.poki-cdn.com/cdn-cgi/image/q=78,scq=50,width=94,height=94,fit=cover,f=auto/83c31a1ddf03ef16ff2c31f73f5fd095/打字-logo.png" srcSet="https://img.poki-cdn.com/cdn-cgi/image/q=78,scq=50,width=94,height=94,fit=cover,f=auto/83c31a1ddf03ef16ff2c31f73f5fd095/打字-logo.png 1x, https://img.poki-cdn.com/cdn-cgi/image/q=78,scq=50,width=188,height=188,fit=cover,f=auto/83c31a1ddf03ef16ff2c31f73f5fd095/打字-logo.png 2x" width="94" height="94" alt="打字游戏" loading="lazy" class="VrWOfVJtTjn2FNJx0TFc" /><span class="QGnVckPD11ZTkQr8o8ci">打字游戏</span></a><a href="/zh/类别" class="DIxbY_Wd8M99mMzbD9Jz Ll7V72dm63WTr1buD4lg"><img src="https://img.poki-cdn.com/cdn-cgi/image/q=78,scq=50,width=94,height=94,fit=cover,f=auto/491499692a2f5a5a970848c80a686661/类别-logo.png" srcSet="https://img.poki-cdn.com/cdn-cgi/image/q=78,scq=50,width=94,height=94,fit=cover,f=auto/491499692a2f5a5a970848c80a686661/类别-logo.png 1x, https://img.poki-cdn.com/cdn-cgi/image/q=78,scq=50,width=188,height=188,fit=cover,f=auto/491499692a2f5a5a970848c80a686661/类别-logo.png 2x" width="94" height="94" alt="所有类别" loading="lazy" class="VrWOfVJtTjn2FNJx0TFc" /><span class="QGnVckPD11ZTkQr8o8ci">所有类别</span></a></div><article class="npmo3Vk8vdpOrUnRlo4K"><div class="ag25MXv4yZahCGrJMxIn"><div class="SIe_wNXliOAsytkgDP1I">关于Poki (宝玩)</div><header class="i3QPWr3keV_hOpU2xsic"><h1 class="Wa2Xpu5vfbxVCjRv2Gv_">免费在线小游戏</h1></header></div><div class="ExURFs1eybHeBRR0Ay6d"><div class="U5UHxulLIj1mqRNKVoIl S9u9oGGPKoCPdp0ckDId"><p>Poki (宝玩) 拥有最丰富的免费在线游戏，从单人休闲到多人合作，致力于为您提供最有趣的游戏体验。打开Poki (宝玩)，即可畅玩所有游戏，无需您下载、登录，更无弹窗干扰。我们的游戏支持台式机、平板电脑、移动设备等多种运行环境。无论是在舒适的家中，还是等车的路边，您都可以通过Poki (宝玩)享受游戏乐趣。每个月有超过 9000 万来自全世界各地的玩家在 Poki (宝玩) 上玩他们最喜爱的游戏。</p>


<h3>我们的游戏</h3>
<p>游戏开发者每天在我们的平台上发布有趣的新游戏。我们最受欢迎的游戏包括像 <a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/g/temple-run-2');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/g/temple-run-2">Temple Run 2</a>、<a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/g/stickman-hook');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/g/stickman-hook">Stickman Hook</a> 和 <a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/g/rodeo-stampede-savannah');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/g/rodeo-stampede-savannah">Rodeo Stampede</a> 这样的热门游戏。这些游戏只能在 Poki (宝玩) 上玩。我们还提供免费玩的经典在线游戏，如 <a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/g/moto-x3m');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/g/moto-x3m">Moto X3M</a>、<a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/g/venge-io');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/g/venge-io">Venge.io</a>、<a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/g/dinosaur-game');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/g/dinosaur-game">Dino Game</a>、<a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/g/smash-karts');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/g/smash-karts">Smash Karts</a>、<a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/g/2048');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/g/2048">2048</a>、<a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/g/penalty-shooters-2');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/g/penalty-shooters-2">Penalty Shooters 2</a> 和 <a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/g/bad-ice-cream');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/g/bad-ice-cream">Bad Ice-Cream</a>。我们共有1000多款游戏供您选择。</p>


<h3>开始游戏</h3>
<p>不确定要玩什么游戏吗？您可以在我们的首页上开启探索之旅，或从以下热门类别中选择一款游戏：</p>
<ul><li><a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/益智');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/益智">益智游戏</a></li><li><a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/双人');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/双人">双人游戏</a></li><li><a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/汽车');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/汽车">汽车游戏</a></li><li><a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/射击');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/射击">射击游戏</a></li><li><a onclick="window.navigateTo('/zh/益智');return false;" href="https://poki.com/zh/益智">益智游戏</a></li></ul>


<h3>Poki (宝玩) 是什么？</h3>
<p>Poki (宝玩) 总部位于阿姆斯特丹，目前有40名员工。团队致力于创建一个免费游戏平台，旨在打造一个向所有人开放的在线游乐场。想了解更多相关信息，请前往我们的 <a href="https://about.poki.com/">公司主页</a> 。如果您是一位游戏开发者，想要您的游戏在网络上取得成功，欢迎您在了解我司信息后，通过 <a href="https://developers.poki.com/">Poki for Developers</a> 与我们联系，期待与您合作。</p></div></div><div class="v8TUHvsE2V93jQeU1nvV"></div></article></div><footer id="footer" class="q3dppPisdqD1gwCqXrlY"><div class="B3Ykv32PAQzAWDm8ZLxP"><div class="gYKLsrGper0lDtd1Jh5L"><div class="NsUjvfZGYVJuaFFoj8UT"><button type="button" aria-label="点击访问Poki (宝玩)的公司页面" class="buttonReset nFfRxeFvFwQzS_6hLEl2"><div class="nDlYEPwiwt1Ocy1EY4QY"><a href="/zh" title="Poki (宝玩)" aria-label="Poki (宝玩)" class="C9JUSu6VaKM5y0Kq4sg2"><span role="img" aria-label="poki" style="--icon-src: url('https://a.poki-cdn.com/icons/ui/poki.svg');" class="kzPaMiKIK5c1hyP3aSiu sWw2o0mSwsqQYurRQt6c"></span></a></div><span class="xYiFDBzvOkiiM3nU6kag"><span class="jX1Y8HMEoQ0MUS7LKDJi">Let the world play</span></span></button></div><div class="Bi9DuiJufrziZoOBS4ZX"><div class="qBUtGmyztDWwGnia_mYq"><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@poki_games" target="_blank" rel="noopener" referrerPolicy="origin" aria-label="Poki TikTok" class="o9xIOU4zSGEaPg5mF5MQ mZsu6pL3yCExNTwxGp3h"></a><a href="https://www.instagram.com/poki__games" target="_blank" rel="noopener" referrerPolicy="origin" aria-label="Poki Instagram" class="o9xIOU4zSGEaPg5mF5MQ A0SVMsfsITinnIFQSmTA"></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Poki" target="_blank" rel="noopener" referrerPolicy="origin" aria-label="Poki YouTube" class="o9xIOU4zSGEaPg5mF5MQ TZVTnwdWUs1jBZcisb_Y"></a></div></div></div><div class="mXTmsEBqPqY4oZrhcK6R"><div class="aAo_lNI7j8nsrF98Hmza"><div class="SlgM_E9RU37FivtI9q1v"><div class="H_XbBqldWkI2_427QKOg">热门</div><a href="/zh/汽车" class="qMWRUBS9td2nFBRm5ow7">汽车游戏</a><a href="/zh/双人" class="qMWRUBS9td2nFBRm5ow7">双人游戏</a><a href="/zh/益智" class="qMWRUBS9td2nFBRm5ow7">益智游戏</a><a href="/zh/all-games" class="qMWRUBS9td2nFBRm5ow7">所有游戏</a></div><div class="SlgM_E9RU37FivtI9q1v